SELECT [t].[WorkStationId], [t].[Pressure], [t].[ProductionLineId], [t].[StationName], [t].[Status], [t].[Temperature], [a].[AlarmId], [a].[MaxPressure], [a].[MaxTemperature], [a].[MinPressure], [a].[MinTemperature], [a].[WorkStationId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [w].[WorkStationId], [w].[Pressure], [w].[ProductionLineId], [w].[StationName], [w].[Status], [w].[Temperature]
    FROM [WorkStations] AS [w]
    WHERE ((([w].[Pressure] >= @__entity_MinPressure_0) AND ([w].[Pressure] <= @__entity_MaxPressure_1)) AND ([w].[Temperature] >= @__entity_MinTemperature_2)) AND ([w].[Temperature] <= @__entity_MaxTemperature_3)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Alarms] AS [a] ON [t].[WorkStationId] = [a].[WorkStationId]
ORDER BY [t].[WorkStationId]
